              <tr>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 rowspan=5><b>Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt</b></td>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Pick up the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt in Lake Rathetear.  It is underwater directly below the flaming Aviak platform.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Diamond</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Drops off random mobs in high level zones.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Jacinth</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Drops off random mobs in high level zones.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Black Sapphire</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Drops off random mobs in high level zones.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Hand in a Diamond, a Black Sapphire, a Jacinth, and the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt to Wenden in East Freeport.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 rowspan=5><b>Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt</b></td>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Damaged Dragon Head Hilt</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Pick up the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt in Timorous Deep (loc -6000, 4000).  It is next to the king piece on the Chessboard.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Ball of Everliving Golem</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Kill the named golems in the Plane of Fear:  Fright, Dread, and Terror.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Giant Monocle</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Kill the Mountain Giant Patriarch in the Dreadlands.  He is a random spawn in the giant fort to the west of Karnor's Castle.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Rejesium Ore</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Giant Monocle to Mentrax Mountainbone in the Frontier Mountains.  He is a named giant in the giant fort, at the end of the mine.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt, the Ball of Everliving Golem, and the Rejesium Ore to Wenden in East Freeport.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 rowspan=6><b>Ancient Sword Blade</b></td>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Rusty Sword Blade</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Talk to Denken Strongpick in the Ocean of Tears (on the Aviak Island, loc 590, -825).  He will tell you about a rusty sword blade he found.  He will also ask you to return some items in exchange for the blade.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Keg of Vox Tail Ale</td>
