              </tr>

              <tr>

                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 rowspan=9><b>Mark of the Sword</b></td>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Wax Sealed Note</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Say [I will do a favor] to Kargak Redblade in East Freeport.  He will hand you a letter to take to Oknoggin in Feerott.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Tiny Lute</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Wax Sealed Note to Oknoggin in the Feerott.  He stands etween the stone bridge and the fallen totem.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>A Book</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Tiny Lute to Kargak Redblade in East Freeport.  He will give you a book to take to his brother, Tenal Redblade, in East Karana.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Frozen Goblin Heart</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Kill ice goblin wizards in Permafrost.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Frozen War Totem</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Hand in the book from Kargak to Tenal Redblade in East Karana (at the very end of the canyon next to the ramp to Highpass).</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Totem of Fiery War</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Frozen War Totem and the Frozen Goblin Heart to Tenal Redblade.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>Green Dragon Scale</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>Kill Severlious in the Emerald Jungle.  The green scale is also dropped by Hoshkar in Veeshan's Peak.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Red Dragon Scale</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Kill Talendor in Skyfire.  The red scale is also dropped by Lord Nagafen in Nagafen's Lair.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>The Mark of the Sword</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Green Dragon Scale, the Red Dragon Scale, and the Totem of Fiery War to Tenal Redblade.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>

                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 rowspan=4><b>Red Scabbard</b></td>

                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Hand of the Maestro</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Kill "a very unpleasant hand" in the Plane of Hate.  It spawns after the Hand of the Maestro is killed.  The Hand of the Maestro spawns after the Maestro of Rancor is killed.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>Note to Kargek</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Mark of the Sword and the Hand of the Maestro to Tenal Redblade to receive a note to take to Kargak Redblade in East Freeport.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=150 align=left>Spiroc Wingblade</td>
                <td background='maroon.jpg' width=300 align=left>Kill the Spiroc Lord in the Plane of Sky.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>Red Scabbard</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>Hand in the Note to Kargek and the Spiroc Wingblade to Kargak Redblade to receive the Red Scabbard and instructions on how to combine the hilts and blades.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>

                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 rowspan=1><b>Jagged Blade of War</b></td>

                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>Jagged Blade of War</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>Combine the Ancient Blade, the Ancient Sword Blade, the Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt, and the Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt in the Red Scabbard to create the Jagged Blade of War (a 2HS weapon).  The sword can be combined in the Red Scabbard to create two 1HS weapons, the Blade of Strategy and the Blade of Tactics.  Combine the two swords to recreate the Jagged Blade of War.</td>
              </tr>

